---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Support Kavu Preservation | Nagayakshi Temple">
  
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="support-hero">
    <div class="support-hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="support-hero-content">
      <h1>Preserve the Sacred Kavus</h1>
      <p>Help protect and restore the seven ancient Sarpa groves for future generations</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Mission -->
  <section class="mission-section">
    <div class="support-container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">Our Sacred Mission</span>
        <h2>Why Kavu Preservation Matters</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mission-content">
        <div class="mission-text">
          <p class="mission-lead">
            The seven sacred Sarpa Kavus are not merely temple property—they are the living homes 
            of the naga deities, the very foundation of this ancient shrine's spiritual power. 
            Without these Kavus, the temple loses its essence.
          </p>
          <p>
            For generations, these sacred groves have provided shelter to the Divine Nagas, acting 
            as portals where devotees' prayers directly reach the serpent deities. But decades of 
            neglect, natural degradation, and the pressures of modern development have threatened 
            their integrity.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Our mission is urgent and clear:</strong> Restore all seven Kavus to their 
            pristine sacred condition before it's too late. This requires replanting native trees, 
            creating protective boundaries, conducting purification rituals, and establishing 
            permanent maintenance systems.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mission-stats">
          <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-number">7</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Sacred Kavus</div>
            <div class="stat-detail">To be fully restored</div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-number">3</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Kavus Restored</div>
            <div class="stat-detail">Through devotee support</div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-number">4</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Remaining</div>
            <div class="stat-detail">Need your help now</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Challenge -->
  <section class="challenge-section">
    <div class="support-container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>The Challenge We Face</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="challenge-grid">
        <div class="challenge-card">
          <div class="challenge-icon">🌳</div>
          <h3>Natural Degradation</h3>
          <p>
            Over decades, many native sacred trees have died or been damaged. Invasive species 
            have taken over. The natural canopy that once sheltered the Kavus has thinned 
            significantly, reducing their spiritual potency.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="challenge-card">
          <div class="challenge-icon">🏗️</div>
          <h3>Development Pressure</h3>
          <p>
            Surrounding land development and construction threaten the boundaries of several Kavus. 
            Without clear demarcation and protective walls, encroachment becomes an ongoing risk.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="challenge-card">
          <div class="challenge-icon">💧</div>
          <h3>Maintenance Needs</h3>
          <p>
            Sacred groves require ongoing care—regular pujas, cleaning, preventing unauthorized 
            entry, and ensuring the sanctity is maintained. This requires dedicated resources 
            and manpower.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="challenge-card">
          <div class="challenge-icon">📿</div>
          <h3>Spiritual Renewal</h3>
          <p>
            Each restored Kavu requires elaborate purification rituals, reinstallation of sacred 
            energies, and continuous worship to maintain its spiritual power as a home for nagas.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How You Can Help -->
  <section class="support-options-section">
    <div class="support-container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">Make an Impact</span>
        <h2>Ways to Support</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="support-grid">
        
        <!-- Kavu Adoption -->
        <div class="support-option featured">
          <div class="option-badge">Most Impactful</div>
          <div class="option-icon">🌳</div>
          <h3>Adopt a Kavu</h3>
          <p class="option-description">
            Take complete responsibility for restoring and maintaining one of the seven sacred 
            Kavus. Your contribution goes toward native tree planting, boundary walls, purification 
            rituals, and ongoing maintenance for one full year.
          </p>
          <div class="option-includes">
            <h4>Includes:</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>200+ native saplings planted</li>
              <li>Protective boundary construction</li>
              <li>Complete purification rituals</li>
              <li>12 months of dedicated maintenance</li>
              <li>Your name displayed at the Kavu</li>
              <li>Special blessings from Ambotti Thampuran</li>
              <li>Annual progress reports with photos</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="option-pricing">
            <div class="price-options">
              <div class="price-tier">
                <span class="tier-name">Full Year Adoption</span>
                <span class="tier-price">₹2,50,000</span>
              </div>
              <div class="price-tier">
                <span class="tier-name">6 Months Adoption</span>
                <span class="tier-price">₹1,50,000</span>
              </div>
              <div class="price-tier">
                <span class="tier-name">3 Months Adoption</span>
                <span class="tier-price">₹75,000</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-support">Adopt a Kavu</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Gau-daanam -->
        <div class="support-option">
          <div class="option-icon">🐄</div>
          <h3>Gau-daanam (Sacred Cow Donation)</h3>
          <p class="option-description">
            Donate a cow to the temple for ongoing milk production used in daily poojas and
            abhishekams. Gau-daanam is considered one of the most meritorious acts in Hindu tradition,
            bringing immense blessings to the donor.
          </p>
          <div class="option-includes">
            <h4>Spiritual Benefits:</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Ancestral blessings and debt repayment</li>
              <li>Progeny blessings for childless couples</li>
              <li>Financial prosperity and stability</li>
              <li>Health and longevity</li>
              <li>Relief from major doshas</li>
              <li>Accumulated punya (merit) for generations</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="option-pricing">
            <div class="price-options">
              <div class="price-tier">
                <span class="tier-name">Full Cow Donation</span>
                <span class="tier-price">₹60,000</span>
              </div>
              <div class="price-tier">
                <span class="tier-name">Half Share</span>
                <span class="tier-price">₹30,000</span>
              </div>
              <div class="price-tier">
                <span class="tier-name">Quarter Share</span>
                <span class="tier-price">₹15,000</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-support">Donate a Cow</a>
        </div>

        <!-- General Donation -->
        <div class="support-option">
          <div class="option-icon">🙏</div>
          <h3>General Temple Support</h3>
          <p class="option-description">
            Support temple operations, daily poojas, maintenance, and preservation activities 
            with a donation of any amount. Every contribution helps maintain the sanctity and 
            traditions of this ancient shrine.
          </p>
          <div class="option-includes">
            <h4>Your donation supports:</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Daily pooja materials and offerings</li>
              <li>Priest salaries and dakshina</li>
              <li>Temple maintenance and upkeep</li>
              <li>Kavu preservation activities</li>
              <li>Festival celebrations</li>
              <li>Free services to poor devotees</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="option-pricing">
            <div class="donation-amounts">
              <button class="amount-btn" data-amount="1000">₹1,000</button>
              <button class="amount-btn" data-amount="5000">₹5,000</button>
              <button class="amount-btn" data-amount="10000">₹10,000</button>
              <button class="amount-btn" data-amount="25000">₹25,000</button>
              <button class="amount-btn custom">Custom</button>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-support">Donate Now</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Monthly Supporter -->
        <div class="support-option">
          <div class="option-icon">📅</div>
          <h3>Monthly Supporter Program</h3>
          <p class="option-description">
            Become a regular monthly supporter of the temple. Your recurring contribution ensures 
            sustained funding for preservation, poojas, and community services. Cancel anytime.
          </p>
          <div class="option-includes">
            <h4>Supporter Benefits:</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Monthly updates on temple activities</li>
              <li>Priority booking for special events</li>
              <li>10% discount on all poojas</li>
              <li>Exclusive access to supporter-only events</li>
              <li>Personal blessings during monthly poojas</li>
              <li>Recognition in annual donor list</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="option-pricing">
            <div class="price-options">
              <div class="price-tier">
                <span class="tier-name">Platinum Supporter</span>
                <span class="tier-price">₹10,000/month</span>
              </div>
              <div class="price-tier">
                <span class="tier-name">Gold Supporter</span>
                <span class="tier-price">₹5,000/month</span>
              </div>
              <div class="price-tier">
                <span class="tier-name">Silver Supporter</span>
                <span class="tier-price">₹2,000/month</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-support">Become a Supporter</a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tax Benefits -->
  <section class="tax-section">
    <div class="support-container">
      <div class="tax-content">
        <h2>Tax Benefits</h2>
        <p class="tax-intro">
          Donations to the temple may be eligible for tax deductions under Section 80G of the 
          Income Tax Act. Consult your tax advisor for specific benefits applicable to your situation.
        </p>
        <div class="tax-grid">
          <div class="tax-item">
            <h4>🧾 Official Receipts</h4>
            <p>All donations receive official receipts with temple seal and signature for tax filing purposes.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tax-item">
            <h4>💳 Secure Payments</h4>
            <p>All online donations processed through secure payment gateways with full encryption.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tax-item">
            <h4>📊 Transparent Use</h4>
            <p>Annual financial reports available showing how donations were utilized for temple activities.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Impact Stories -->
  <section class="impact-section">
    <div class="support-container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">Real Impact</span>
        <h2>What Your Support Achieves</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="impact-grid">
        <div class="impact-card">
          <div class="impact-image">
            <img src="/images/temple1.jpg" alt="Restored Kavu" style="filter: sepia(0.2);">
          </div>
          <div class="impact-content">
            <h3>Shankarodath Kavu Restoration</h3>
            <p class="impact-year">Completed 2023</p>
            <p>
              Through devotee contributions, we successfully restored the main Shankarodath Kavu—
              planting 250 native trees, constructing protective walls, and conducting elaborate 
              purification ceremonies. The Kavu is now thriving with renewed spiritual energy.
            </p>
            <div class="impact-stats-mini">
              <span>250 trees planted</span>
              <span>2,000 sq ft protected</span>
              <span>Daily poojas established</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="impact-card">
          <div class="impact-image">
            <img src="/images/temple.jpg" alt="Temple cow" style="filter: sepia(0.2);">
          </div>
          <div class="impact-content">
            <h3>Gau Shala (Cow Shelter)</h3>
            <p class="impact-year">Ongoing Project</p>
            <p>
              Through Gau-daanam contributions, we now maintain 8 cows providing fresh milk for
              daily abhishekams and poojas. The Go Shala has become self-sustaining, with excess 
              milk distributed free to poor families in surrounding villages.
            </p>
            <div class="impact-stats-mini">
              <span>8 cows maintained</span>
              <span>50L daily milk</span>
              <span>200 families served</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="impact-card">
          <div class="impact-image">
            <img src="/images/Divine%20connection.jpg" alt="Free prasadam" style="filter: sepia(0.2);">
          </div>
          <div class="impact-content">
            <h3>Free Services Fund</h3>
            <p class="impact-year">Annual Program</p>
            <p>
              Monthly supporter contributions enable us to provide free poojas to economically 
              disadvantaged devotees who cannot afford ritual costs but desperately need spiritual 
              help. Over 500 devotees served annually.
            </p>
            <div class="impact-stats-mini">
              <span>500+ devotees helped</span>
              <span>Free poojas</span>
              <span>No one turned away</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="cta-container">
      <h2>Every Contribution Makes a Difference</h2>
      <p class="cta-text">
        Whether you adopt a Kavu, donate a cow, or contribute ₹1,000—every offering helps 
        preserve this ancient sacred tradition for future generations. The nagas bless those 
        who protect their homes.
      </p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-cta-primary">Contact to Donate</a>
        <a href="tel:+919946373522" class="btn-cta-secondary">Call: +91 9946373522</a>
      </div>
      <p class="cta-note">
        For large donations, corporate CSR partnerships, or specific project sponsorships, 
        please contact Ambotti Thampuran directly.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
/* Support Page Styles */
.support-hero {
  position: relative;
  min-height: 60vh;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  background: 
    linear-gradient(rgba(82, 14, 9, 0.88), rgba(82, 14, 9, 0.88)),
    url('/images/temple1.jpg') center/cover;
  padding: 8rem 2rem 4rem;
  text-align: center;
}

.support-hero-overlay {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
}

.support-hero-content {
  max-width: 800px;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 10;
}

.support-hero h1 {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 4.5rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: white;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
}

.support-hero p {
  font-size: 1.4rem;
  color: var(--gold-light);
  line-height: 1.6;
  font-weight: 500;
}

.support-container {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 2rem;
}

.section-header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
}

.section-label {
  display: inline-block;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: var(--gold);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 3px;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  font-weight: 600;
}

.section-header h2 {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 3rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--laterite-red);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

/* Mission Section */
.mission-section {
  padding: 6rem 2rem;
  background: var(--bg-base);
}

.mission-content {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr;
  gap: 4rem;
  align-items: start;
}

.mission-lead {
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  line-height: 1.9;
  color: var(--laterite-dark);
  font-weight: 500;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.mission-text p {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  line-height: 1.9;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.mission-text strong {
  color: var(--laterite-red);
}

.mission-stats {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  position: sticky;
  top: 6rem;
}

.stat-card {
  background: var(--bg-alt);
  padding: 2rem;
  border-radius: 15px;
  text-align: center;
  border-left: 5px solid var(--laterite-red);
}

.stat-number {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 4rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--laterite-red);
  line-height: 1;
}

.stat-label {
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--laterite-dark);
  margin-top: 0.5rem;
}

.stat-detail {
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  margin-top: 0.5rem;
}

/* Challenge Section */
.challenge-section {
  padding: 6rem 2rem;
  background: var(--bg-alt);
}

.challenge-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
  gap: 2.5rem;
}

.challenge-card {
  background: var(--bg-base);
  padding: 2.5rem;
  border-radius: 15px;
  box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  text-align: center;
}

.challenge-icon {
  font-size: 4rem;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.challenge-card h3 {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 1.6rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--laterite-red);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.challenge-card p {
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  line-height: 1.8;
  color: var(--text-muted);
}

/* Support Options */
.support-options-section {
  padding: 6rem 2rem;
  background: var(--bg-base);
}

.support-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
  gap: 3rem;
}

.support-option {
  background: var(--bg-alt);
  padding: 3rem;
  border-radius: 20px;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  position: relative;
}

.support-option.featured {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff9e6 0%, #fffaf0 100%);
  border: 3px solid var(--gold);
}

.option-badge {
  position: absolute;
  top: -15px;
  right: 20px;
  background: var(--laterite-red);
  color: white;
  padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
  border-radius: 25px;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(122, 25, 18, 0.3);
}

.option-icon {
  font-size: 4rem;
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.support-option h3 {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 2rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--laterite-red);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  text-align: center;
}

.option-description {
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  line-height: 1.8;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.option-includes {
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.option-includes h4 {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--laterite-dark);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.option-includes ul {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
}

.option-includes li {
  padding: 0.6rem 0;
  padding-left: 2rem;
  position: relative;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
}

.option-includes li:last-child {
  border-bottom: none;
}

.option-includes li::before {
  content: '✓';
  position: absolute;
  left: 0;
  color: var(--laterite-red);
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 1.2rem;
}

.option-pricing {
  background: var(--bg-base);
  padding: 2rem;
  border-radius: 12px;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.price-options {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1rem;
}

.price-tier {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 1rem;
  background: var(--bg-alt);
  border-radius: 8px;
}

.tier-name {
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--text-muted);
}

.tier-price {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--laterite-red);
}

.donation-amounts {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 1rem;
}

.amount-btn {
  padding: 1rem;
  border: 2px solid var(--laterite-red);
  background: var(--bg-base);
  color: var(--laterite-red);
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-weight: 600;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.amount-btn:hover {
  background: var(--laterite-red);
  color: white;
}

.amount-btn.custom {
  grid-column: 1 / -1;
  background: var(--gold);
  border-color: var(--gold);
  color: var(--text-muted);
}

.btn-support {
  display: block;
  padding: 1.2rem;
  background: var(--laterite-red);
  color: white;
  text-align: center;
  text-decoration: none;
  border-radius: 2px;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.btn-support:hover {
  background: var(--saffron);
  transform: translateY(-3px);
}

/* Tax Section */
.tax-section {
  padding: 4rem 2rem;
  background: var(--laterite-dark);
}

.tax-content {
  text-align: center;
}

.tax-content h2 {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--gold-light);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.tax-intro {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  color: var(--bg-alt);
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto 3rem;
  line-height: 1.8;
}

.tax-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
  gap: 2rem;
}

.tax-item {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  padding: 2rem;
  border-radius: 15px;
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
}

.tax-item h4 {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  color: var(--gold-light);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.tax-item p {
  color: var(--bg-alt);
  line-height: 1.7;
}

/* Impact Section */
.impact-section {
  padding: 6rem 2rem;
  background: var(--bg-alt);
}

.impact-grid {
  display: grid;
  gap: 3rem;
}

.impact-card {
  background: var(--bg-base);
  border-radius: 20px;
  overflow: hidden;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 400px 1fr;
  gap: 0;
